Juji Community in Chikun local government area of the state. The bandits also killed a vigilante during the operation. The kidnappers reportedly invaded the community at about 10:00 p.m., on January 24.  Vanguard WHAT could have resulted in a repeat of the Chibok and Dapchi school girls’ abductions was averted in Zamfara State on Wednesday night when bandits stormed Government Girls Comprehensive Secondary School, Moriki in Zurmi Local Council of Zamfara State. May 3, 2019 In "Headlines" Suspected kidnappers have killed four policemen in Jankasa village, Rigasa, Igabi local government area of Kaduna State. August 13, 2018 In "Crime Guard" The Zamfara State Police Command said on Sunday it had killed a notorious kidnapper, arrested eight others and recovered arms. February 25, 2018 In "News"